---
title: Spiced Apple Lentil Stew with Homemade Croutons and Pepitas
description: Perfumed by warm spices and sweetened with veggies and apple, this hearty and comforting stew is pure heaven. The crunchy croutons and pepitas take this over the top!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-apple-lentil-stew-eb7cd6e2.jpg
